"{\"uid\": \"bnn-news.com-macron-has-a-backup-plan-for-opening-ceremony-of-olympic-games-should-security-require-it-256105\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"French President Emmanuel Macron said in an interview with BFM TV and RMC radio on Monday, the 15th of April, that France has backup plans in place in case of security concerns over the organisation of the opening ceremony of the Olympic Games in the River Seine on the 26th of July, with conflicts in the Middle East and Ukraine and the threat of terrorist attacks, prompting the French government to step up security measures, reportsReuters.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 444, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 16, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"French President\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_France\"}, {\"begin\": 17, \"end\": 32, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Emmanuel Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\"}, {\"begin\": 59, \"end\": 65, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BFM_TV\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"BFM TV\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BFM_TV\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BFM_TV\"}, {\"begin\": 70, \"end\": 79, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RMC_(France)\", \"score\": 0.999999989573098, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"RMC radio\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RMC_(France)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RMC_(France)\"}, {\"begin\": 115, \"end\": 121, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"s